      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional E92 M3, preserved in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral dynamics. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement with VAC-coated shells and upgraded throttle actuators, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly is within factory tolerances. The exterior retains its original factory depth with no discernible orange peel, and the carbon fiber roof remains free of UV degradation or delamination. An uncompromising example for the discerning driver who values mechanical purity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
