      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most fastidious collector. This car has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its original showroom depth and clarity. There are no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found; the paint has been preserved with a multi-stage ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule\u2014the leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free from typical bolster wear or UV fading, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every switch, dial, and digital interface operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule at authorized service centers. All original documentation, spare keys, and a comprehensive service history binder are included. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of this model that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
